## Decisions Made
- enqueue accepts both space-separated WI IDs (argparse nargs="+") and comma-separated within a single arg, matching the pre-script SKILL.md examples (`WI-014` and `WI-018,WI-019,WI-020`).
- Used a `targets[]` array within native_task_sync for batch updates rather than emitting one hint per WI; this gives the orchestrator a single hint object to iterate over.
- clear --reason demoted's idempotency guard checks all four conditions (status=ready, branch null, commit null, promotion.status=not_ready) — if any WI partially demoted, the work-items.json write happens to ensure consistency.

